{"tid":799071,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2018-19 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃參賽32人名單公佈及抽籤詳情","createTime":"2018-08-29T18:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T18:42:48.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9677491840344645ba10f81e460754087132873","tid":799071,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"經過咗兩回合附加賽既激烈大戰之後,最後四個分組賽名額都塵埃落定啦<br />\n現定喺8月31日晚上8時40分進行抽籤,根據往年經驗直播其實無乜人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以今年就唔搞咁多野啦,抽完我會再開post公佈分組安排,敬請留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注: 同一種子(POT),同一國家不會被抽進同一小組<br />\n<br />\n18-19環球女神冠軍盃參賽名單<br />\nPOT1:<br />\n新垣結衣/日本<br />\nIU/韓國<br />\n劉亦菲/中國<br />\n周子瑜@TWICE/台灣<br />\n朱千雪/香港<br />\nElizabeth Olsen/美國<br />\nGal Gadot/以色列<br />\n林明禎/馬來西亞<br />\n<br />\nPOT2:<br />\n石原聰美/日本<br />\n宮脇咲良@HKT48/日本<br />\nJessica Alba/美國<br />\n李一桐/中國<br />\n李佳芯/香港<br />\nOksana Neveselaya/白俄羅斯<br />\nEmma Watson/英國<br />\n裴柱現@Red Velvet/韓國<br />\n<br />\nPOT3:<br />\n鄭家純/台灣<br />\n宋智孝/韓國<br />\nOom Eisaya/泰國<br />\n苟芸慧/香港<br />\nNatalie Portman/以色列<br />\nEmilia Clarke/英國<br />\n朱主愛/馬來西亞<br />\n何念茲/馬來西亞<br />\n<br />\nPOT4:<br />\nManoban@BLACKPINK/泰國<br />\nSarah Gadon/加拿大<br />\nRachel McAdams/加拿大<br />\nAdelaide Kane/澳洲<br />\n迪麗熱巴/中國<br />\n謝安琪/香港<br />\n林潤娥@少女時代/韓國<br />\nAlexandra Daddario/美國<br />\n<br />\n多謝巴絲打既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0308d46a65342ddd3cf450305912b9901aaf64","tid":799071,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94289e78a978704673c63d769c6eaf136cd1584b","tid":799071,"uid":92376,"like":0,